headline: DOW Launches Polymer Processing Aid Solution for Safer Packaging
summary: Dow unveils DOWSIL 5-1050, a safer, fluoropolymer-free solution for high-quality packaging films with regulatory compliance.

headline: PPG Benefits From Cost Actions and Acquisitions, Weak Demand Ails
